                                This project is the subject of the data structures and algorithms module.
                                It used knowledge of linklist, tree and arrays of pointers.</p>
                        </div>
                        <button class="text-blue-500 border border-blue-500 rounded-xl p-2 mt-3
                                hover:text-white hover:bg-blue-500">
